    <briefdescription>
<para>Basic Audio Profile stream structure. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Streams represents a stream configuration of a Remote Endpoint and a Local Capability.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>Streams are unidirectional but can be paired with other streams to use a bidirectional connected isochronous stream. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
